173 A.3d 600 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. A.D., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND S.R. AND J.M., DEFENDANTS. IN THE MATTER OF A.D.-R. AND N.R., MINORS-RESPONDENTS.

C-305 September Term 2017

079264 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000642-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
